501
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:12,680
Don't scare me,

502
00:32:13,350 --> 00:32:14,110
Qing.

503
00:32:19,550 --> 00:32:20,200
Ji Chu,

504
00:32:21,240 --> 00:32:23,240
