for the empress.

507
00:32:28,270 --> 00:32:29,030
I know, Qing.

508
00:32:30,270 --> 00:32:31,160
As long as you say the word,

509
00:32:32,240 --> 00:32:33,070
I'll always believe you,

510
00:32:33,640 --> 00:32:34,510
